Name: Issue Invoice

Short Description: Once a customer wants to pay the waiter will issue an invoice.

Precondition: An open invoice for the customer exists.

Postcondition: The invoice is closed and can not be edited any more.

Error Condition: No open invoice exists.

System state on error condition: No invoice is issued.

Actors: Waiter

Trigger: Customer wishes to pay.

Standard procedure:
(1) Customer has consumed goods.
(2) Customer wishes to pay.
(3) Waiter closes invoice.
(4) Customer pays.
(5) Customer leaves.